rows.label: qev085601_MSG0001
rows.name: Colonel? You haven't seen Lao around, have you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0002
rows.name: Not recently, no.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0003
rows.name: Did you two have plans?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0004
rows.name:
Not plans, so much as a mission we were
supposed to handle together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0005
rows.name: And he stood you up? Ugh, that's so tacky![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0006
rows.name: Heh. Can't really argue with that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0007
rows.name:
Still, I'm sure he had his reasons,
so try not to be too harsh on him, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0008
rows.name:
Wait, what? Why are you defending
the guy who stood you up?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0009
rows.name: ...Another fair point.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0010
rows.name: You are such a weirdo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0010_2
rows.name: What's the deal? Why're you so protective of Lao, anyway?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0011
rows.name:
We go way back. We were in the same unit
before serving under the colonel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0012
rows.name: Wow, that long?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0013
rows.name: Yep. I was a scout, and he was a sniper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0014
rows.name:
We fought all over the world before
the Coalition Government formed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0015
rows.name: Man, I bet there are some stories there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0016
rows.name: Yeah, not sure I want anyone hearing 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0017
rows.name:
Hey, Elma, what do you think?
Maybe we can help Doug out since Lao was a no-show?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0018
rows.name: I certainly don't mind. Is it something we could manage?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0019
rows.name:
Oh, well, sure. It's nothing that requires
a Pathfinder specifically.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0020
rows.name: If you all want to help, I'd gladly take it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0021
rows.name: Okay then, Tatsu on the case. Doug can rest easy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0022
rows.name: Heh. That's reassuring.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0023
rows.name: We're heading to Noctilum?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0024
rows.name:
Right. Three days ago, we started picking up
scattered UM responses in the area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0025
rows.name: These are the spots.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0025_2
rows.name:
Problem is, we can't run our usual
analysis through FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0026
rows.name: So you want us to check them out in person?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0027
rows.name: Exactly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0028
rows.name: If you can take these three, my team will handle the others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0033
rows.name: Sounds like a piece of cake![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0034
rows.name: We'll get in touch once we've gathered the data.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0035
rows.name: That'll be perfect, thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0036
rows.name:
HQ is offering a reward, of course, but either way,
drinks are on me once you're done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_JNK0010
rows.name: Grin

rows.label: qev085601_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Doug he'd better know a good place.

rows.label: qev085601_JNK0020
rows.name: Frown

rows.label: qev085601_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Doug you'd really prefer cash.

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0037
rows.name: Are you kidding? Of course I do! Just leave it to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0038
rows.name: We'll be looking forward to it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0039
rows.name:
Geez, cut a working class guy some slack, will ya?
I never pegged you as the greedy type![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0040
rows.name: Hey, it's not greed if we earn it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085601_MSG0041
rows.name: That's... Well, all right, whatever. Fair enough.[ST:wait ]
